bpp/descriptor.name: UNIZAP
bpp/descriptor.short_desc: unizap Seller Marketplace all in one solution
bpp/descriptor.long_desc: Unizap empowers businesses to create, manage, and upscale online stores with ease. Its user-friendly interface and advanced features enable entrepreneurs to build captivating websites, showcase products, and provide customers with a seamless shopping experience at lightning speed.

descriptor.name: Masala Dosa
